&lt;li&gt;Support the administration and ongoing improvement of benefits and pension programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage payroll systems and tools, including SAP integration, to support efficient and reliable payroll operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
